text: Henri Landheer (27 April 1899 - 15 March 1958) was a Dutch long-distance runner. He competed in the marathon at the 1928 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1899 births Category:1958 deaths Category:Athletes (track and field) at the 1928 Summer Olympics Category:Dutch male long- distance runners Category:Dutch male marathon runners Category:Olympic athletes of the Netherlands Category:People from Veendam
